# Technical Specification: GreenCity Offset Ledger - Credit Rebalancing Module

**Document ID:** MS-ARCH-GCOL-2026-052-REBALANCE-V1  
**Author:** Senior Technical Architect, Meridian Systems  
**Date:** [Current Date]  
**Version:** 1.0  
**Project Phase:** Third-party integration (Phase 2 of 3)  
**Client Approval Status:** Pending Review  
**Scope:** This specification introduces a credit rebalancing module to the GreenCity Offset Ledger, extending the future-projections and verification workflow modules (from MS-ARCH-GCOL-2026-052-FUTURE-PROJ-V1 and MS-ARCH-GCOL-2026-052-VERIF-UPDATE-V1). The module automates deficit absorption for self-attested remediation projects that fail to materialize within 12 months of the planned completion date. Upon detection, the system transfers the reserved credit deficit to the city's general public-works environmental ledger, maintaining the industrial partner's compliance standing during the reconciliation period. Detection and rebalancing are handled via scheduled jobs, with audit trails for all actions. This design integrates with existing entities (e.g., PlannedRemediationInvestment, CreditReservation) and assumes client-authorized criteria for "failure" (e.g., status not "Completed"). Implementation uses the existing PostgreSQL database, with triggers and cron jobs for automation. No policy changes are proposed; this is a technical implementation blueprint.

## 1. Data Model Updates

The data model is extended to include entities for deficits, rebalancing events, and the city's general ledger. JSON Schemas are provided for new and updated entities. The 12-month window is calculated from `plannedCompletionDate` in PlannedRemediationInvestment, with failure defined as status not reaching "Completed" by that threshold.

### 1.1 New Entity Schemas

#### DeficitRecord
Tracks deficits arising from failed reservations.
```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "deficitId": { "type": "string", "description": "Unique identifier (UUID)", "example": "def-12345678-90ab-cdef-1234-567890abcdef" },
    "reservationId": { "type": "string", "description": "Reference to CreditReservation" },
    "facilityId": { "type": "string", "description": "Reference to Facility" },
    "deficitAmount": { "type": "number", "description": "Deficit in metric tons CO2e (equals reservedAmount)" },
    "detectionDate": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time", "description": "Timestamp when deficit was detected" },
    "status": { "type": "string", "enum": ["Detected", "Absorbed", "Resolved", "Disputed"], "description": "Deficit status" },
    "notes": { "type": "string", "description": "Details on failure reason (e.g., 'Project not completed within 12 months')" }
  },
  "required": ["deficitId", "reservationId", "facilityId", "deficitAmount", "detectionDate", "status"]
}
```

#### RebalancingEvent
Logs each rebalancing action, including absorption into the city's ledger.
```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "eventId": { "type": "string", "description": "Unique identifier (UUID)", "example": "evt-abcdef12-3456-7890-abcd-ef1234567890" },
    "deficitId": { "type": "string", "description": "Reference to DeficitRecord" },
    "absorptionDate": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time", "description": "Timestamp of absorption" },
    "absorbedAmount": { "type": "number", "description": "Amount absorbed into city's ledger in metric tons CO2e" },
    "ledgerEntryId": { "type": "string", "description": "Reference to CityLedgerEntry" },
    "status": { "type": "string", "enum": ["Initiated", "Completed", "Failed"], "description": "Event status" }
  },
  "required": ["eventId", "deficitId", "absorptionDate", "absorbedAmount", "ledgerEntryId", "status"]
}
```

#### CityLedgerEntry
Represents entries in the city's general public-works environmental ledger for absorbed deficits.
```json
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "entryId": { "type": "string", "description": "Unique identifier (UUID)", "example": "led-13579ace-2468-bdf0-1234-56789abcdef0" },
    "entryDate": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time", "description": "Timestamp of ledger entry" },
    "amount": { "type": "number", "description": "Absorbed amount in metric tons CO2e (positive for deficits)" },
    "sourceType": { "type": "string", "enum": ["DeficitAbsorption", "PublicWorksCredit", "Other"], "description": "Type of entry" },
    "description": { "type": "string", "description": "Description of the entry", "example": "Absorbed deficit from facility fac-123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000" },
    "reconciliationPeriod": { "type": "string", "description": "Associated reconciliation period (e.g., 'FY2025')", "example": "FY2025" }
  },
  "required": ["entryId", "entryDate", "amount", "sourceType", "description", "reconciliationPeriod"]
}
```

